### Job Controller Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:8083/api/jobs
### Note: X-User-Id header simulates authenticated employer user

### Prerequisites: Create categories and skills first
### 1. Create Job Category (run JobCategoryController.http first)
### 2. Create Job Skills (run JobSkillController.http first)

### 1. Create a new Job (Full Time, Remote)
POST http://localhost:8083/api/jobs
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 1

{
  "title": "Senior Java Developer",
  "description": "We are looking for an experienced Java developer to join our team",
  "requirements": "5+ years of Java experience, Spring Boot knowledge required",
  "responsibilities": "Develop and maintain microservices, code review, mentor junior developers",
  "benefits": "Competitive salary, health insurance, remote work",
  "companyId": 1,
  "categoryId": 1,
  "skillIds": [1, 2, 3],
  "tagIds": [1],
  "address": "123 Tech Street",
  "city": "San Francisco",
  "state": "CA",
  "country": "USA",
  "zipCode": "94105",
  "minSalary": 120000,
  "maxSalary": 180000,
  "jobType": "FULL_TIME",
  "workMode": "REMOTE",
  "experienceLevel": "SENIOR_LEVEL",
  "openings": 2,
  "applicationDeadLine": "2026-08-31",
  "expiresAt": "2026-12-31"
}

### 2. Create another Job (Contract, Hybrid)
POST http://localhost:8083/api/jobs
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 1

{
  "title": "Python Data Scientist",
  "description": "Looking for a data scientist to work on ML projects",
  "requirements": "Python, Machine Learning, SQL",
  "responsibilities": "Develop ML models, data analysis, visualization",
  "benefits": "Flexible hours, learning budget",
  "companyId": 1,
  "categoryId": 1,
  "skillIds": [6],
  "tagIds": [2, 3],
  "address": "456 Data Avenue",
  "city": "New York",
  "state": "NY",
  "country": "USA",
  "zipCode": "10001",
  "minSalary": 100000,
  "maxSalary": 160000,
  "jobType": "CONTRACT",
  "workMode": "HYBRID",
  "experienceLevel": "MID_LEVEL",
  "openings": 1,
  "applicationDeadLine": "2026-09-15",
  "expiresAt": "2026-11-30"
}

### 3. Create another Job (Part Time, On-site)
POST http://localhost:8083/api/jobs
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 2

{
  "title": "Junior Frontend Developer",
  "description": "Entry-level position for frontend development",
  "requirements": "HTML, CSS, JavaScript basics",
  "responsibilities": "Develop UI components, fix bugs, write tests",
  "benefits": "Training program, mentorship",
  "companyId": 1,
  "categoryId": 1,
  "skillIds": [2],
  "tagIds": [1, 4],
  "address": "789 Frontend Lane",
  "city": "Austin",
  "state": "TX",
  "country": "USA",
  "zipCode": "78701",
  "minSalary": 50000,
  "maxSalary": 70000,
  "jobType": "PART_TIME",
  "workMode": "ON_SITE",
  "experienceLevel": "ENTRY_LEVEL",
  "openings": 3,
  "applicationDeadLine": "2026-09-30",
  "expiresAt": "2026-10-31"
}

### 4. Get Job by ID (1)
GET http://localhost:8083/api/jobs/1

### 5. Get Job by ID (2)
GET http://localhost:8083/api/jobs/2

### 6. Get Job by ID (3)
GET http://localhost:8083/api/jobs/3

### 7. Get all Jobs with default search
GET http://localhost:8083/api/jobs

### 8. Get all Jobs with search - filter by city
GET http://localhost:8083/api/jobs?city=San%20Francisco

### 9. Get all Jobs with search - filter by job type
GET http://localhost:8083/api/jobs?jobType=FULL_TIME

### 10. Get all Jobs with search - filter by work mode
GET http://localhost:8083/api/jobs?workMode=REMOTE

### 11. Get all Jobs with search - filter by experience level
GET http://localhost:8083/api/jobs?experienceLevel=SENIOR_LEVEL

### 12. Get Jobs by Company ID (1)
GET http://localhost:8083/api/jobs/company/1

### 13. Get all Jobs as Admin
GET http://localhost:8083/api/jobs/admin

### 14. Update Job (1) - Change title and description
PUT http://localhost:8083/api/jobs/1
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 1

{
  "title": "Lead Java Developer (Updated)",
  "description": "Looking for a lead Java developer to manage team",
  "requirements": "7+ years of Java experience, team management skills",
  "responsibilities": "Lead development team, architecture decisions, code review",
  "benefits": "Competitive salary, health insurance, remote work, stock options",
  "companyId": 1,
  "categoryId": 1,
  "skillIds": [1, 2, 3],
  "tagIds": [1],
  "address": "123 Tech Street",
  "city": "San Francisco",
  "state": "CA",
  "country": "USA",
  "zipCode": "94105",
  "minSalary": 150000,
  "maxSalary": 220000,
  "jobType": "FULL_TIME",
  "workMode": "REMOTE",
  "experienceLevel": "LEAD",
  "openings": 1,
  "applicationDeadLine": "2026-08-31",
  "expiresAt": "2026-12-31"
}

