### 16. Publish Job (1)
PATCH http://localhost:8083/api/jobs/1/publish
X-User-Id: 1

### 17. Publish Job (2)
PATCH http://localhost:8083/api/jobs/2/publish
X-User-Id: 1

### 18. Publish Job (3)
PATCH http://localhost:8083/api/jobs/3/publish
X-User-Id: 2

### 19. Close Job (1)
PATCH http://localhost:8083/api/jobs/1/close
X-User-Id: 1

### 20. Get Job (1) after closing
GET http://localhost:8083/api/jobs/1

### 21. Try to update job with wrong employer ID (should fail)
PUT http://localhost:8083/api/jobs/2
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 999

{
  "title": "Unauthorized Update",
  "description": "This should fail",
  "requirements": "None",
  "responsibilities": "None",
  "benefits": "None",
  "companyId": 1,
  "categoryId": 1,
  "skillIds": [],
  "tagIds": [],
  "address": "Street",
  "city": "City",
  "state": "State",
  "country": "Country",
  "zipCode": "12345",
  "minSalary": 50000,
  "maxSalary": 80000,
  "jobType": "FULL_TIME",
  "workMode": "REMOTE",
  "experienceLevel": "JUNIOR",
  "openings": 1,
  "applicationDeadLine": "2026-09-15",
  "expiresAt": "2026-12-31"
}

### 22. Try to close job with wrong employer ID (should fail)
PATCH http://localhost:8083/api/jobs/2/close
X-User-Id: 999

### 23. Try to publish already published job
PATCH http://localhost:8083/api/jobs/2/publish
X-User-Id: 1

